{
  "texts": [
    "Monster also provides compliance reports for NIST, HIPAA and other standards.",
    "OSSIM does not provide such reports.",
    "Support for adding new data sources is another important feature that allows the customization of a SIEM system.",
    "All SIEMs come with a set of built-in parsers and decoders for the logs of various devices.",
    "At times, the users may want to parse logs of a device that is not supported by SIEM by default."
  ]
}